\begin_inset Formula 
\[
N^{*}=\frac{1}{b}-\left(\frac{bW}{a}\right)^{1/\sigma}\frac{1}{bW}.
\]

\end_inset

Thus 
\begin_inset Formula $N^{*}$
\end_inset

